description:
One day Candyman walked in a music store. He went missing for two weeks after that. Then appeared the illustrious Galileo the Funky Saxman, or at least that's how he introduced himself after giving East Shine City an unforgettable night of mindbogglingly intergalactic saxophone solos.

- The Galileo the Funky Saxman colorway. An outfit aligned with the planets.
- The Saturnus Incognita colorway. A fitting look for an infamous partyman.
- Saxophone sounds when playing with either of the colorways.
name: Galileo The Funky Saxman Outfit for Candyman
